OL,6,FA Welsh business owner says she "will
OL,7,Flose #15,000" due to changes in
OL,8,Fbusiness rate relief.
OL,10,FBusinesses in Wales have given a cold
OL,11,Fresponse to the cut in rate relief
OL,12,Fwhich dropped from 75% to 40% in Wales
OL,13,Ffrom the start of April 2024.
OL,15,FLauren Evans, managing director and co-
OL,16,Fowner of Fablas Ice Cream, said: "The
OL,17,Fdifference in the business rate relief
OL,18,Ffor Fablas alone would be
OL,19,Fapproximately #15,000 across the four
OL,20,Fstores around our production unit.
