OL,6,F"That is massive. That's a part-time
OL,7,Fmember of staff's wages in an economic
OL,8,Fclimate where we know jobs are scarce."
OL,10,FLauren, who oversees branches in
OL,11,FPenarth, Cowbridge, Porthcawl and
OL,12,FCaerphilly, claims are being "unfairly
OL,13,Ftargeted" when the relief in England
OL,14,Fis remaining at 75%.
OL,16,FShe added: "It really is tough, and
OL,17,Fyou are just thinking what exactly are
OL,18,Fyou gaining from being a business
OL,19,Fowner? It is a massive strain on you
OL,20,Fmentally and on the business."
