OL,6,FMeanwhile, inone accommodation
OL,7,Fprovider says she is struggling to hit
OL,8,Fthe Welsh Government's 182-day rule
OL,9,Ffor self-catering holiday lets to be
OL,10,Fable to pay business rates rather than
OL,11,Fdomestic rates.
OL,13,FThe criteria says holiday lets must be
OL,14,Ffilled for 182 days a year ` up from a
OL,15,Fprevious 70 - in order to qualify for
OL,16,Fbusiness rates.
OL,18,FJenny Williams, owner of the The
OL,19,FLaundry Retreat, said the business is
OL,20,Freaching the 182-day mark by the skin
OL,21,Fof its teeth.
