OL,6,FShe said: "I think because it is in a
OL,7,Frolling basis as well, you're
OL,8,Fpressured into making sure you're
OL,9,Fgoing throughout the winter months
OL,10,Ftoo, so we are having to come up with
OL,11,Fways of bringing people in which means
OL,12,Fgiving offers and that's where we're
OL,13,Flosing money instead of making it.
OL,15,F"North-east Wales is not a honey pot
OL,16,Fdestination where we are here. We are
OL,17,Fnot in a very busy striving place, a
OL,18,Fdestination where everyone is drawn
OL,19,Fto. So, we've got to try a bit harder
OL,20,Fto bring people to us."
