OL,6,FBut with costs rising for businesses,
OL,7,FWelsh Government budgets are not going
OL,8,Fas far either.
OL,10,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"We are very aware that the ongoing
OL,12,Fcost-of-living and cost-of-doing-
OL,13,Fbusiness crises continue to present
OL,14,Fdifficulties for small and independent
OL,15,Fbusinesses in all sectors across the
OL,16,Fcountry.
OL,18,F"We are doing all we can, with the
OL,19,Fresources and powers available to us,
OL,20,Fto provide support in these difficult
OL,21,Ftimes.
